@node History "IconDT History"

  @{b}@{u}History@{uu}@{ub}

      @{b}Version 39.0@{ub} - initial release.

      @{b}Version 39.1@{ub}

    Bug fixes:
    À Enforcerhit removed, thanks goes to Carsten Klein

      @{b}Version 39.2@{ub}

    Improvements:
    À Preferences with ENV-value for the screenmode

      @{b}Version 39.3@{ub}

    Improvements:
    À Prefences moved to ENV:Datatypes/
    À Renamed into "icon.prefs"
    À New setting: "PURE" shows only the icon

      @{b}Version 39.4@{ub}

    Improvements:
    À IconDT supports now DTpref2.0+ for the setting of the preferences

    Bug fixes:
    À EMail-address changes

      @{b}Version 40.1@{ub}

    Improvements:

    À IconDT complete rewritten, because I killed the orginal sourcecode :-(
    À IconDT complete localizied
    À Uses now the screenfont
    À All entrys could be switched off

    Bug fixes:
    À SMail-address changed

      @{b}Version 40.2@{ub}

    Improvements:

    À New entry: ½position╗, which will show the icon-position. Idea by Matthias Kraft
    À Font could be selected by the user
    À Runs only with DTpref4.0 or above
    À Protection bits will now also show the Group- and Other-Flags

    Bug fixes:
    À Select cheme changed. Now the unselected image will be viewed at least.
@endnode

